        </item>
        <item>
            <title>《Dead Island: Riptide》Steam 限時免費    《Dead Island 2》4 月登陸 Steam</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/14/dead-island-riptide-free/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dead-island-riptide-free</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/14/dead-island-riptide-free/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 09:00:41 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Dead Island]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Dead Island:RIptide]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Deep Silver]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[steam]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Techland]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1219992</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《Dead Island 2》預計 4 月在 Steam 開售，發行商 Deep Silver 今日起至 2 月 16 日提供前作《Dead Island: Riptide Definitive Edition》限時免費，玩家只需要有 Steam 帳户就可以免費遊玩這款喪屍遊戲。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1219994" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot2024021413-1-686x580.jpg" alt="" width="686" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot2024021413-1-686x580.jpg 686w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot2024021413-1.jpg 1064w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 686px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220004" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_480f620579dbf5514-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_480f620579dbf5514-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_480f620579dbf5514.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1219993" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot2024021413-694x143.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="143" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot2024021413-694x143.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot2024021413.jpg 777w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《Dead Island》系列遊戲是一款恐怖動作角色扮演電子遊戲，系列第一款遊戲《Dead Island》於 2011 年上市，遊戲設定是玩家在島嶼度假村裏遇到喪屍襲擊。是次限時免費的《Dead Island: Riptide Definitive Edition》屬遊戲系列第二集作品，故事背景是前作的生還者抵達另一座島嶼，豈料該島嶼也被喪屍侵佔，玩家需要殺出重圍，逃離喪屍島。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1219997" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_77915e22ac2e68187-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_77915e22ac2e68187-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_77915e22ac2e68187.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1219998" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_4a2cb7f338dcceab8-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_4a2cb7f338dcceab8-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_4a2cb7f338dcceab8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1219999" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_e342b08361265af64-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_e342b08361265af64-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_e342b08361265af64.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220000" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_55cf5d81b4ac85d2e-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_55cf5d81b4ac85d2e-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_55cf5d81b4ac85d2e.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220001" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_81b4d0a1cc1512c80-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_81b4d0a1cc1512c80-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_81b4d0a1cc1512c80.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220002" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_d0ac6f8e16e69a331-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_d0ac6f8e16e69a331-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_d0ac6f8e16e69a331.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220003" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_b49eaf85a07aaef60-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_b49eaf85a07aaef60-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_b49eaf85a07aaef60.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220005" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_e026a2f2800af5cef-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_e026a2f2800af5cef-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_e026a2f2800af5cef.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>遊戲系列最新作品《Dead Island 2》命途多舛，開發期間多次延遲發布日期，最終在 2023 年 4 月正式發售，PC 版由 Epic Games 獨佔一年。目前 Steam 表示將會在今年 4 月 22 日在平台發售《Dead Island 2》。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220006" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_0ffbf23f87d25032c-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_0ffbf23f87d25032c-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ss_0ffbf23f87d25032c.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/383180/Dead_Island_Riptide_Definitive_Edition/">Steam</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/06/granblue-fantasy-relink-review/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】《Granblue Fantasy: Relink》 角色陣容多可玩性高 + 四人合作爽快打怪</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/29/palworld-review/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】《Palworld》　開放式世界生存 + 捕捉寵物分工合作</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/21/avatar-frontiers-of-pandora-reviews/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】《阿凡達：潘朵拉邊境》    新遊戲引擎打造 + 科幻題材畫面逼真</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/14/dead-island-riptide-free/game-channel/">《Dead Island: Riptide》Steam 限時免費    《Dead Island 2》4 月登陸 Steam</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
